      • closest_distance_group

        int closest_distance_group​(int id1,
                           estado.centerOrGroup center_or_group,
                           java.util.LinkedList<java.lang.Integer> remainingGroups,
                           int npersonas)
        Out of the groups in remaining groups returns the closest group to the given group
        Parameters:
        id1 - identifier of the group where we are
        center_or_group - does the identifier id1 belong to a center or to a group
        remainingGroups - list of the remaining groups not yet asigned
        npersonas - personas que el helicoptero contiene
        Returns:
        identifier of the closest group, return -1 if there isn't a possible closest group
